ğŸ“˜ E2E Automation Project â€” Playwright + Pytest + Allure

Automated endâ€‘toâ€‘end test for eBay, built with:
- Playwright (Python)
- Pytest
- Allure reporting
- Page Object Model

The test flow includes:
1 Opening the eBay homepage
2 Performing an advanced search
3 - Opening several product pages
  - Selecting random item variations
  - Adding items to the cart
4 Verifying that the total does not exceed a defined limit

ğŸš€ How to Run the Project
Prerequisites
Make sure the following are installed:
- Python 3.10+
- pip
- Playwright
Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

Install Playwright browsers
playwright install

Run tests
pytest

ğŸ“Š Reports
Allure Results
Allure is already integrated via:
--alluredir=allure-results

After running tests, a folder will appear:
allure-results/

This is sufficient for the assignment.
Installing Allure CLI is optional.
Optional: HTML Report
pytest --html=report.html


Optional: JUnit XML Report
pytest --junitxml=report.xml

